8 §62. Membership; officers and terms of office
9 A. The council shall be composed of nineteen twenty-one members. as
10 follows:
11 (1) Six Eight members of the council shall be comprised as follows:
12 (a) The governor of Louisiana, or his designee.
13 (b) The adjutant general of Louisiana, or his designee.
14 (c) The president of the Louisiana State Senate, or a state senator designated
15 by the president.
16 (d) The speaker of the Louisiana House of Representatives, or a state
17 representative designated by the speaker.
18 (e) The secretary of Louisiana Economic Development, or his designee.
19 (f) The secretary of the Department of Veterans Affairs, or his designee.
20 (g) The chair of the Senate Select Committee on Military and Veterans
21 Affairs, or his designee.
